{"tid":1975151,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"真攬炒系列18: 零售管理協會推算2至5月將有過萬名零售業員工失業","createTime":"2020-04-16T10:40:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T10:53:37.000Z","uid":292292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"05c5e8599972251604826a48d9a6b1d9264e7ce5","tid":1975151,"uid":292292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T10:40:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1520987-20200416.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1520987-20200416.htm&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10IeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=d20693ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1520987-20200416.htm&h=c97655e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1520987-20200416.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n零售管理協會調查推算，2月至5月期間，全港將會有超過1萬名零售業員工失業，5至8月有6600間店舖因公司無力經營而要結業。有超過8成零售商認為目前的減租幅度及深度不足。 協會向業主提出，應跟隨政府寬減至少75%租金，為期至少半年；又或是按營業額一定比例來計算租金，同樣維持至少半年。<br />\n<br />\n協會表示，今次的調查在3月30至4月9日期間進行，而第二輪防疫抗疫基金在4月8日公布，因此調查未能充分反映業界對第二輪措施的意見。今次調查收到152間零售公司回覆，中小企佔當中6成，涉及3300多間零售店舖，僱員人數達59000多人，約佔整個零售業員工23％。<br />\n<br />\n第二輪防疫抗疫基金提出保就業措施，補貼僱主支薪一半、上限9000元，政府提出僱主選擇1至3月任何一個月為工資基礎。零售管理協會主席謝邱安儀表示，從社會事件開始，零售業僱員的佣金收入已大減，縱使選擇有較好表現的1月，都難以反映對僱員的影響。"},{"pid":"95f5fa42e328cce2f5dd5155eed0588cf14abf09","tid":1975151,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T10:45:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/proxy/zKpePcTKba3yQCSHtovKR7Ded-q7gswrkI8nvGxjHMjNTSngPDBQLnPhlMxYil_GfXICGOdKf-ZinnxC-79SLfpw5VETfa89PyVd-IAMK74cSvS2TvLoYF6syE_SvfDh8yazG35fTdQOt8WG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2Fproxy%2FzKpePcTKba3yQCSHtovKR7Ded-q7gswrkI8nvGxjHMjNTSngPDBQLnPhlMxYil_GfXICGOdKf-ZinnxC-79SLfpw5VETfa89PyVd-IAMK74cSvS2TvLoYF6syE_SvfDh8yazG35fTdQOt8WG&h=1f8f78ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d9e01aefe5b9447d95a0edec62b93eab788f3af","tid":1975151,"uid":65598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T10:53:37.000Z","msg":"死左膠無尾BEAR (#292292) 死五毛屈手足<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1601170/page/38\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1601170/page/38</a><br />\n留言881開始屈手足亂打人, 但又無證據<br />\n<br />\n&quot;依家係無証據話廢老先打人， 但有証據前線打人呀， 你有片既請share出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我同你say sorry&quot;"}]}